      "matters": "PETITION FOR PROBATE OF WILL AND FOR LETTERS TESTAMENTARY<br>Off Calendar Dec-24-2008 Granted Per Written Order<br>MINI MINUTES: Appearances: George Sullivan for Rita Kitchner.<br><br>The Court stated that the matter was on for probate of the lost will, that proper notice was given, that an appearance was required, and that counsel was present. There being no objection, the Court granted the petition for Probate of Will and For Letters Testamentary (signing an order for the same in open court). The will was admitted and the bond was set at $10,000. <br><br>Judge Pro Temp: Sue M. Kaplan. Reporter: Katy Bersamin, CSR#11722. Clerk: Jackie Alameda/Rosie Noguera.  <br>",
